.TH ZDOROVO 1 "13 July 2026" "Zdorovo 0.1.5" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
zdorovo \- guided health breaks and local screen-time analytics
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B zdorovo
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B Zdorovo
runs configurable eye, movement and posture reminders during active computer
work. The desktop application also provides breathing sessions, habit tracking
and local per-application analytics.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \--background
Start tracking without opening the main window.
.TP
.B \--trigger KIND
Open a reminder immediately. KIND is one of eyes, general, neck, drops, back,
wrists, breathing or water.
.TP
.B \--version
Print the installed version.
.TP
.B \-h, \--help
Show command-line help.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/zdorovo/config.json
User settings.
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/zdorovo/usage.sqlite3
Screen-time, exercise, habit and wellbeing history.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR systemctl (1),
.BR gnome-extensions (1)
